ential type category" }, "fullDescription": { "text": "The value of an expression shall not be assigned to an object of a different essential type category [MISRAC2025-RULE_10_3-b]" }, "defaultConfiguration": { "level": "error" }, "help": { "text": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_10_3-b.html", "markdown": "[The value of an expression shall not be assigned to an object of a different essential type category \\[MISRAC2025-RULE_10_3-b\\]](https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_10_3-b.html)" }, "helpUri": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_10_3-b.html", "properties": { "tags": [ "MISRA C 2025", "Rule 10.3 (Required) The value of an expression shall not be assigned to an object with a narrower essential type or of a different essential type category" ] } }, { "id": "MISRAC2025-RULE_10_4-a", "name": "Both operands of an operator in which the usual arithmetic conversions are performed shall have the same essential type category", "shortDescription": { "text": "Both operands of an operator in which the usual arithmetic conversions are performed shall have the same essential type category" }, "fullDescription": { "text": "Both operands of an operator in which the usual arithmetic conversions are performed shall have the same essential type category [MISRAC2025-RULE_10_4-a]" }, "defaultConfiguration": { "level": "error" }, "help": { "text": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_10_4-a.html", "markdown": "[Both operands of an operator in which the usual arithmetic conversions are performed shall have the same essential type category \\[MISRAC2025-RULE_10_4-a\\]](https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_10_4-a.html)" }, "helpUri": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_10_4-a.html", "properties": { "tags": [ "MISRA C 2025", "Rule 10.4 (Required) Both operands of an operator in which the usual arithmetic conversions are performed shall have the same essential type category" ] } }, { "id": "MISRAC2025-RULE_18_1-a", "name": "Avoid accessing arrays out of bounds", "shortDescription": { "text": "Avoid accessing arrays out of bounds" }, "fullDescription": { "text": "Avoid accessing arrays out of bounds [MISRAC2025-RULE_18_1-a]" }, "defaultConfiguration": { "level": "error" }, "help": { "text": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.flow\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_18_1-a.html", "markdown": "[Avoid accessing arrays out of bounds \\[MISRAC2025-RULE_18_1-a\\]](https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.flow\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_18_1-a.html)" }, "helpUri": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.flow\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_18_1-a.html", "properties": { "tags": [ "MISRA C 2025", "Rule 18.1 (Required) A pointer resulting from arithmetic on a pointer operand shall address an element of the same array as that pointer operand" ] } }, { "id": "MISRAC2025-RULE_21_10-b", "name": "The time handling functions and macros of the library <time.h> shall not be used", "shortDescription": { "text": "The time handling functions and macros of the library <time.h> shall not be used" }, "fullDescription": { "text": "The time handling functions and macros of the library <time.h> shall not be used [MISRAC2025-RULE_21_10-b]" }, "defaultConfiguration": { "level": "error" }, "help": { "text": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_21_10-b.html", "markdown": "[The time handling functions and macros of the library <time.h> shall not be used \\[MISRAC2025-RULE_21_10-b\\]](https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_21_10-b.html)" }, "helpUri": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_21_10-b.html", "properties": { "tags": [ "MISRA C 2025", "Rule 21.10 (Required) The Standard Library time and date functions shall not be used" ] } }, { "id": "MISRAC2025-RULE_21_10-c", "name": "The types defined in the library <time.h> shall not be used", "shortDescription": { "text": "The types defined in the library <time.h> shall not be used" }, "fullDescription": { "text": "The types defined in the library <time.h> shall not be used [MISRAC2025-RULE_21_10-c]" }, "defaultConfiguration": { "level": "error" }, "help": { "text": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_21_10-c.html", "markdown": "[The types defined in the library <time.h> shall not be used \\[MISRAC2025-RULE_21_10-c\\]](https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_21_10-c.html)" }, "helpUri": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_21_10-c.html", "properties": { "tags": [ "MISRA C 2025", "Rule 21.10 (Required) The Standard Library time and date functions shall not be used" ] } }, { "id": "MISRAC2025-RULE_8_7-a", "name": "Functions and objects should not be defined with external linkage if they are referenced in only one translation unit", "shortDescription": { "text": "Functions and objects should not be defined with external linkage if they are referenced in only one translation unit" }, "fullDescription": { "text": "Functions and objects should not be defined with external linkage if they are referenced in only one translation unit [MISRAC2025-RULE_8_7-a]" }, "defaultConfiguration": { "level": "warning" }, "help": { "text": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.global\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_8_7-a.html", "markdown": "[Functions and objects should not be defined with external linkage if they are referenced in only one translation unit \\[MISRAC2025-RULE_8_7-a\\]](https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.global\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_8_7-a.html)" }, "helpUri": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.global\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_8_7-a.html", "properties": { "tags": [ "MISRA C 2025", "Rule 8.7 (Advisory) Functions and objects should not be defined with external linkage if they are referenced in only one translation unit" ] } }, { "id": "MISRAC2025-RULE_8_4-a", "name": "A declaration shall be visible when an object or function with external linkage is defined", "shortDescription": { "text": "A declaration shall be visible when an object or function with external linkage is defined" }, "fullDescription": { "text": "A declaration shall be visible when an object or function with external linkage is defined [MISRAC2025-RULE_8_4-a]" }, "defaultConfiguration": { "level": "error" }, "help": { "text": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_8_4-a.html", "markdown": "[A declaration shall be visible when an object or function with external linkage is defined \\[MISRAC2025-RULE_8_4-a\\]](https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_8_4-a.html)" }, "helpUri": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_8_4-a.html", "properties": { "tags": [ "MISRA C 2025", "Rule 8.4 (Required) A compatible declaration shall be visible when an object or function with external linkage is defined" ] } }, { "id": "MISRAC2025-RULE_8_2-c", "name": "Function types shall be in prototype form", "shortDescription": { "text": "Function types shall be in prototype form" }, "fullDescription": { "text": "Function types shall be in prototype form [MISRAC2025-RULE_8_2-c]" }, "defaultConfiguration": { "level": "error" }, "help": { "text": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_8_2-c.html", "markdown": "[Function types shall be in prototype form \\[MISRAC2025-RULE_8_2-c\\]](https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_8_2-c.html)" }, "helpUri": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_8_2-c.html", "properties": { "tags": [ "MISRA C 2025", "Rule 8.2 (Required) Function types shall be in prototype form with named parameters" ] } }, { "id": "MISRAC2025-RULE_1_5-c", "name": "Function types shall be in prototype form", "shortDescription": { "text": "Function types shall be in prototype form" }, "fullDescription": { "text": "Function types shall be in prototype form [MISRAC2025-RULE_1_5-c]" }, "defaultConfiguration": { "level": "error" }, "help": { "text": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_1_5-c.html", "markdown": "[Function types shall be in prototype form \\[MISRAC2025-RULE_1_5-c\\]](https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_1_5-c.html)" }, "helpUri": "https:\/\/localhost:8443\/grs\/dtp\/rulesdoc\/com.parasoft.xtest.cpp.analyzer.static.pattern\/10.7.3\/MISRAC2025-RULE_1_5-c.html", "properties": { "tags": [ "MISRA C 2025", "Rule 1.5 (Required) Obsolescent language features shall not be used" ] } }, { "id": "MISRAC2025-RULE_12_1-a", "name": "Use paren